Project Rules:
- Prefer absolute imports rooted at `/home/flaccagora/Desktop/genesis_tests`.
- Keep Python style Black-compatible (PEP 8, 88-char soft limit); run formatters when touching files.
- New/modified functions require type hints for parameters and return types.
- Training/experiment scripts must rely on config globals + `utils/configurator.py` overrides instead of argparse.
- Default logger stack: enable Weights & Biases (wandb) and TensorBoard unless explicitly disabled in config.
- When integrating new features, update config defaults plus matching files under `config/` for discoverability.
- Activate genesis conda environment before installing packages and running scripts
